{"tid":1117113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱黑雨嗰陣我屌到個00後跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-04-20T12:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T14:08:11.000Z","uid":150100,"like":141,"dislike":1190,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"5003066eb3c96bd3606009c519529dc67e354836","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁話說本少爺係真男人嚟<br />\n識我嘅都知無論雨勢幾大<br />\n我出街都係唔會好似啲懦夫咁擔住把遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁所以即使頭先落到狗屎咁<br />\n我都係戴住耳機，雙手插袋咁迎住風雨而行<br />\n正當我享受緊依種男人嘅瀟灑<br />\n突然間有把遮遮鳩住我<br />\n我拎轉頭一望<br />\n有個一睇就知係00後嘅柒頭話咩遮埋我一齊行<br />\n我屌你老母，嗰嘢即刻火都嚟埋，一嘢將把遮拍落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n00後：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話你遮乜撚柒鳩嘢？<br />\n未撚見過真男人呀？<br />\n屌你老母臭閪男人老狗擔乜春遮<br />\n雨水都驚你切咗碌柒佢做女人啦屌你老母<br />\n返屋企扮barbie玩hello kitty啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n然後個00後開始喊咁樣<br />\n我就更加火撚滾<br />\n佢滴眼淚未滴出嚟<br />\n我就即刻喝鳩佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n點知條撚樣真係即刻跪喺度喊住嗌daddy mummy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就話屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n落個雨就要擔遮，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我就覺得反正啲00後都冇得救<br />\n屌嚟都嘥gas就雙手插袋走咗去<br />\n留低個柒頭喺度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd44e99216e4f12d4b8847b0716d590d65cea175","tid":1117113,"uid":71508,"like":46,"dislike":139,"score":-93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"00後唔屌唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577486454cab877bb68a1128da5d1bea5d6cb09b","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":18,"dislike":112,"score":-94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"連仔好應該po依個post上ig<br />\n等大家知道啲00後係幾咁不堪"},{"pid":"a6ae907ed29efe97568c6b17f9d9175d512cd23b","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"dd44e99216e4f12d4b8847b0716d590d65cea175","tid":1117113,"uid":71508,"like":46,"dislike":139,"score":-93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"00後唔屌唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19dae8872c013e64763d320ad2eb735b83743b82","tid":1117113,"uid":202621,"like":18,"dislike":88,"score":-70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"666skrskr"},{"pid":"8e904713bed3ce98fc7db8bf5c39e72d195cbe1d","tid":1117113,"uid":179979,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<br />\n<br />\n今日全日係室內"},{"pid":"b617e13cbde7325adf3d45a131995f5e5a9b57a6","tid":1117113,"uid":1435,"like":3,"dislike":35,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"屌得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n00後唔屌唔得"},{"pid":"efe68a8f589ebf8f8a1187fbe0fe492dca0638e2","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":92,"dislike":9,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"19dae8872c013e64763d320ad2eb735b83743b82","tid":1117113,"uid":202621,"like":18,"dislike":88,"score":-70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"666skrskr"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"返大陸啦00後大陸仔<br />\n信唔信我屌到你跪喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50067af52a559031a687a8112a8d3421cb85d911","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"9個00後負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6602bc0df55077134552f54ae201bf4254f66131","tid":1117113,"uid":76074,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78763df9bffa4789a991688f0f94a3378f65a805","tid":1117113,"uid":199900,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"樓主光頭未"},{"pid":"415b01b9e44450abef8649e68d3d3894212c3fec","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6602bc0df55077134552f54ae201bf4254f66131","tid":1117113,"uid":76074,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"文盲？？"},{"pid":"57027b6e65dcf53a79fffe1226bb3072b0fcb1bf","tid":1117113,"uid":145273,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"假膠<br />\n分分鐘樓主係俾人屌到喊嗰嗰00後"},{"pid":"bf75368889c45313389419b99789583014b7fa99","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮<br />\n估唔到00後已經攻陷連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c7916b1f6cca2bfcac5324359b88f866da3368","tid":1117113,"uid":76074,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0c6c4d081de47387bd24b9ede5ff6cea9604967","tid":1117113,"uid":112355,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"好型呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.