dy mummy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就話屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n落個雨就要擔遮，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我就覺得反正啲00後都冇得救<br />\n屌嚟都嘥gas就雙手插袋走咗去<br />\n留低個柒頭喺度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"72f27744ff0366785d24900624da4c1c375c9fee","tid":1117113,"uid":198615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"樓主拎白卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333436bb59e149218db9a51977c80044d529527f","tid":1117113,"uid":151695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬頭先係咪比雷劈撚到傻閪左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2891b95efbfd5dd0c48e90ea9a918cf851db8e0e","tid":1117113,"uid":202621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe68a8f589ebf8f8a1187fbe0fe492dca0638e2","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":92,"dislike":9,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"19dae8872c013e64763d320ad2eb735b83743b82","tid":1117113,"uid":202621,"like":18,"dislike":88,"score":-70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"666skrskr"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"返大陸啦00後大陸仔<br />\n信唔信我屌到你跪喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"ching牛b死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddca41864f9cf1d399f65fdf3bae73a6fe53e952","tid":1117113,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"係咪撞鬼呀"},{"pid":"438f9400941c847b77a1e5903920f4994d007fe0","tid":1117113,"uid":239565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim