r />\n我話你遮乜撚柒鳩嘢？<br />\n未撚見過真男人呀？<br />\n屌你老母臭閪男人老狗擔乜春遮<br />\n雨水都驚你切咗碌柒佢做女人啦屌你老母<br />\n返屋企扮barbie玩hello kitty啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n然後個00後開始喊咁樣<br />\n我就更加火撚滾<br />\n佢滴眼淚未滴出嚟<br />\n我就即刻喝鳩佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n點知條撚樣真係即刻跪喺度喊住嗌daddy mummy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就話屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n落個雨就要擔遮，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我就覺得反正啲00後都冇得救<br />\n屌嚟都嘥gas就雙手插袋走咗去<br />\n留低個柒頭喺度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"有無叫個00後幫你含埋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"非基不了"},{"pid":"71c242a8aa9f5c7d2fff8b33f51306bc64f8b1c0","tid":1117113,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497c8eda6e8a294a861b36ce9d82b9922ae40b32","tid":1117113,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"993b5d7d3537717c9c085ba38a8afae859ff62f1","tid":1117113,"uid":111814,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"本來都覺得寫得幾好，但冇是咁的，零分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"邊個話真人真事唔使加是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aee105b976dd9f0b08f98813a119c90e93a3dea","tid":1117113,"uid":165677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20